statements: SELECT * FROM swimmer_feedback;
SELECT swimmer_id, coach_evaluation FROM swimmer_feedback WHERE rating > 3;
SELECT coach_evaluation, rating FROM swimmer_feedback WHERE swimmer_id = 2;
SELECT judge_evaluation FROM swimmer_feedback WHERE rating < 2 ORDER BY swimmer_id DESC;
SELECT id, swimmer_id, rating FROM swimmer_feedback WHERE coach_evaluation IS NOT NULL;
SELECT * FROM swimmer_feedback WHERE swimmer_id = 1 ORDER BY rating DESC;
SELECT swimmer_id, coach_evaluation FROM swimmer_feedback WHERE rating > 4.5;
SELECT id, judge_evaluation FROM swimmer_feedback WHERE coach_evaluation LIKE '%good%';
SELECT swimmer_id, rating FROM swimmer_feedback WHERE rating < 3 OR rating > 4 ORDER BY swimmer_id ASC;
SELECT id, judge_evaluation, rating FROM swimmer_feedback WHERE id BETWEEN 5 AND 10;
SELECT * FROM SwimmerFeedback WHERE SwimmerID = 1;
SELECT Feedback FROM SwimmerFeedback WHERE CoachID = 5;
SELECT SwimmerID, CoachID, Feedback FROM SwimmerFeedback WHERE SwimmerID = 3 AND CoachID = 7;
SELECT SwimmerID, Feedback FROM SwimmerFeedback WHERE CoachID = 2 ORDER BY SwimmerID DESC;
SELECT SwimmerID, CoachID, Feedback FROM SwimmerFeedback WHERE CoachID = 4 AND SwimmerID IN (2, 5);
SELECT * FROM SwimmerFeedback WHERE CoachID = 1;
SELECT SwimmerID, CoachID, Feedback FROM SwimmerFeedback ORDER BY CoachID DESC;
SELECT SwimmerID, MAX(CoachID) AS MaxCoachID FROM SwimmerFeedback GROUP BY SwimmerID;
SELECT AVG(Rating) AS AvgRating, COUNT(EvaluationID) AS NumEvaluations FROM PerformanceEvaluation WHERE SwimmerID = 2;
SELECT JudgeID, COUNT(EvaluationID) AS NumEvaluations FROM PerformanceEvaluation GROUP BY JudgeID HAVING COUNT(EvaluationID) > 1;
SELECT * FROM Swimmers;
SELECT id, name, age, gender FROM Swimmers WHERE age > 20;
SELECT name, gender, coach_feedback FROM Swimmers WHERE gender = 'Male';
SELECT * FROM Coaches WHERE experience_years > 5;
SELECT id, name, specialization FROM Coaches WHERE specialization = 'Synchronized Swimming';
SELECT * FROM Swimmers WHERE age > 20 ORDER BY name DESC;
SELECT id, name, gender FROM Swimmers WHERE gender = 'Female';
SELECT * FROM Coaches WHERE experience_years >= 5 AND specialization != 'Swimming';
SELECT id, name, overall_evaluation FROM Judges WHERE affiliation = 'National Federation';
SELECT id, name, specialization FROM Coaches WHERE experience_years < 10 ORDER BY specialization ASC;
SELECT * FROM Swimmers;
SELECT swimmer_name, swimmer_age FROM Swimmers ORDER BY swimmer_age DESC;
SELECT swimmer_name, swimmer_gender FROM Swimmers WHERE swimmer_gender = 'Male';
SELECT coach_name, coach_specialty FROM Coaches WHERE coach_specialty = 'Diving';
SELECT judge_name, judge_expertise FROM Judges ORDER BY judge_expertise ASC;
SELECT * FROM Swimmers ORDER BY swimmer_age DESC;
SELECT swimmer_name, swimmer_gender FROM Swimmers WHERE swimmer_age > 20;
SELECT coach_name, coach_specialty FROM Coaches WHERE coach_specialty = 'Swimming';
SELECT judge_name, judge_expertise FROM Judges WHERE judge_expertise LIKE '%Diving%';
SELECT Swimmers.swimmer_name, Evaluations.feedback, Evaluations.score FROM Swimmers JOIN Evaluations ON Swimmers.swimmer_id = Evaluations.swimmer_id;
SELECT * FROM Swimmers WHERE age > 20;
SELECT name, gender FROM Swimmers WHERE level = 'Intermediate';
SELECT id, name, experience_years FROM Coaches ORDER BY experience_years DESC;
SELECT id, name, affiliation FROM Judges WHERE affiliation LIKE '%International%';
SELECT swimmer_id, coach_id, judge_id, overall_score FROM Feedback WHERE overall_score >= 8;
SELECT * FROM Swimmers WHERE age > 25 ORDER BY name DESC;
SELECT name, gender, age FROM Swimmers WHERE gender = 'Male' AND level = 'Advanced';

SELECT Swimmers.name, Coaches.name, feedback.overall_score FROM Swimmers JOIN Feedback ON Swimmers.id = Feedback.swimmer_id JOIN Coaches ON Feedback.coach_id = Coaches.id WHERE feedback.overall_score > 8 ORDER BY feedback.date DESC;

SELECT Judges.name, PerformanceEvaluations.performance_score, PerformanceEvaluations.comments FROM Judges JOIN PerformanceEvaluations ON Judges.id = PerformanceEvaluations.judge_id WHERE PerformanceEvaluations.performance_score < 5;

SELECT Swimmers.name, Coaches.specialty, Feedback.comments FROM Swimmers JOIN Coaches ON Swimmers.id = Coaches.id JOIN Feedback ON Coaches.id = Feedback.coach_id WHERE Feedback.comments LIKE '%improve%' ORDER BY Feedback.date ASC;
